  "detailed_description": "Set a course for fast-paced fun in Shop-n-Spree: Shopping Paradise! Your tropical island home has fallen on hard times, but you’ve come up with a plan to turn things around. With the help of the local community, you set out to build and run a series of amazing internationally-themed malls! Serve customers, upgrade stores, and create new items as you turn the island into the world’s premier shopping destination in this exciting time-management game!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Unique gameplay<br />\r\n- Fast-paced fun<br />\r\n- Amazing internationally-themed malls!",
  "about_the_game": "Set a course for fast-paced fun in Shop-n-Spree: Shopping Paradise! Your tropical island home has fallen on hard times, but you’ve come up with a plan to turn things around. With the help of the local community, you set out to build and run a series of amazing internationally-themed malls! Serve customers, upgrade stores, and create new items as you turn the island into the world’s premier shopping destination in this exciting time-management game!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Unique gameplay<br />\r\n- Fast-paced fun<br />\r\n- Amazing internationally-themed malls!",
